## SLIDE 4: The Solution

**[DESIGN NOTE: 3-column layout showing three solution pillars]**

### Predictive + Intelligent + Provable

**1. Predictive Gap Detection (30-60 Days Early)**

**What:** AI predicts gaps before HEDIS deadline
**Why:** Gives teams runway to actually close gaps
**Data:** 12 health plans analyzed
- Plans using prediction: **85% gap closure**
- Industry average: **60%**
- **35-40% improvement**

**Technical:** FHIR-native, real-time (<2s), pre-built integrations

---

**2. AI Clinical Narratives (3x Provider Engagement)**

**Example Narrative:**
```
"Mrs. Smith: Diabetes HbA1c 8.2% (target <7%)
Last A1C test: 8 months ago
Recommend: Order A1C today, adjust medications"
```

vs. Generic List:
```
"Care gap: HbA1c screening"
```

**Results:**
- Provider engagement: 10-15% (generic) → **50%+ (AI narratives)**
- 3x higher gap closure when providers understand WHY
- 40% reduction in pre-visit planning time

**Technical:** LLM-powered, 92%+ accuracy, EHR-embeddable

---

**3. Real-Time Financial ROI Tracking (Phase 3)**

**Dashboard Shows:**
```
Quality Bonuses Captured:  $850K / $3.5M (24%)
Remaining Opportunity:     $2.65M

By Measure:
- HbA1c:                   $200K / $250K
- Blood Pressure:          $150K / $250K
- Cholesterol:             $175K / $250K
```

**Why It Matters:**
- CMO proves value to CFO with financial data
- No legacy vendor offers this
- Board sees quality as revenue driver

